---
// Testimonials section component
---

<section id="testimonios" class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-black">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gray-800 text-blue-300 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6 border border-gray-700">
        <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mr-2"></span>
        Lo Que Dicen Nuestros Clientes
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-6">
        Historias de Éxito
        <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-blue-600">
          Reales
        </span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Descubre cómo empresas como la tuya han transformado sus operaciones y multiplicado su rentabilidad 
        con nuestras soluciones de automatización.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <!-- Testimonial 1 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-blue-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">MR</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-white">María Rodríguez</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">CEO, TechSolutions</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic leading-relaxed">
          "EM STUDIOS automatizó nuestro proceso de facturación. Lo que antes nos tomaba un día completo, 
          ahora se hace automáticamente en 1 hora. Hemos reducido errores al 98% y ahorrado 15 horas semanales."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-green-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500 to-green-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">CF</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-white">Carlos Fernández</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Director IT, RetailMax</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic leading-relaxed">
          "La automatización de nuestro control de inventario ha sido excelente. Alertas automáticas, reportes en tiempo real 
          y mejor organización. Hemos mejorado nuestra eficiencia en un 60%."
        </blockquote>
      </div>

      <!-- Testimonial 3 -->
      <div class="bg-gray-900 rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-700 hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-cyan-500/20 transition-all duration-300">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-6">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mr-4">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-lg">AL</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-heading font-bold text-white">Ana López</h4>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Gerente General, LogiCorp</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex mb-4">
          {[...Array(5)].map(() => (
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-yellow-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
              <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
            </svg>
          ))}
        </div>
        <blockquote class="text-gray-300 italic leading-relaxed">
          "El equipo de EM STUDIOS no solo automatizó nuestros procesos, sino que nos acompañó en toda la transformación. 
          Profesionales excepcionales con resultados garantizados."
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 